descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a reference shape, which will be the shape with the most blocks, with various colored blocks to its sides.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same size.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... replicate the reference shape, using the color of the other  blocks as a start point and then replicate that pattern to the edge of the grid, even if it needs a incomplete shape.
